So, what happens when you put it in the microwave? Water-boiling steam explosions?!

00:00:28.996 --> 00:00:30.996
*theme song plays*

00:00:29.796 --> 00:00:31.796
Jory: Let's go roast some nuts!

00:00:30.929 --> 00:00:32.929
Jory: And, as always, our Sharp microwave!

00:00:32.399 --> 00:00:34.399
Jory: It's never a good idea, unless you want an explosion!

00:00:34.401 --> 00:00:36.401
Jory: Stopping, stopping!

