 balloon and a red balloon will explode at the same exact time!

00:03:19.332 --> 00:03:22.330
Jon: Here's the irony, though- the water comes from separate water fountains!

00:03:23.825 --> 00:03:28.820
That's brutal! My prediction passed, I'm sorry, folks. I failed miserably...

00:03:28.542 --> 00:03:30.540
Jon: It looks bigger than it did before!

00:03:30.811 --> 00:03:32.810
Jory: Oh, yeah! The top part is definitely...

00:03:32.079 --> 00:03:34.080
Jon: Oh! Here it comes! Here it comes, dude!

00:03:34.948 --> 00:03:37.950
Jory: Aw! If only we had put it in there for, like, another minute!

00:03:38.018 --> 00:03:40.020
Jon: It's almost there!

00:03:38.919 --> 00:03:42.920
Jory: Come on! Oh, it's a race against time!

00:03:43.056 --> 00:03:45.060
Jon: 14 seconds left...

00:03:44.351 --> 00:03:46.350
*balloon pops*

00:03:45.187 --> 00:03:47.190
Jory: Oh! It did! It did it!

00:03:46.793 --> 00:03:48.790
Jon: Awesome!

00:03:50.263 --> 00:03:52.260
Jon: With only five seconds left on the clock!

00:03:52.165 --> 00:03:54.160
Jory: I'm gonna kill it.

00:03:53.546 --> 00:03:55.550
Okay, let's open this bad boy up!

00:03:56.069 --> 00:03:59.070
Jon: Yup, that's a lotta steam! But it's just water! That's okay to inhale!

00:03:59.005 --> 00:04:08.000
Jory: I'm so dumb right now! I know that, in order for that balloon to expand, this water would 
have had to have been boiling. Now, I'm just reaching in there with pretty much my bare hands!

00:04:09.282 --> 00:04:14.280
Jory: Look at all this steam coming out right now! 'Cause that's what 
 we do here at "Is it a Good Idea to Microwave This?"

00:04:14.387 --> 00:04:16.390
Jon: We turn water into a gas!

00:04:16.859 --> 00:04:18.860
Jory: That is a LOT of water! 

00:04:18.358 --> 00:04:21.360
Jon: You filled the balloon up! What do you expect?! 
Did you think it was just gonna go somewhere?!

00:04:21.461 --> 00:04:23.460
Jory: Aaugh! That's BOILING water!

00:04:23.175 --> 00:04:25.180
Jon: You didn't think this one through, did ya?

00:04:24.297 --> 00:04:27.300
Listen, my PRODUCERS didn't think this one through, okay?

00:04:28.435 --> 00:04:30.440
Jon: Hey! YOU suggested it!

00:04:29.569 --> 00:04:31.570
I'm just talent! Talent's dumb! I'm dumb!

00:04:32.405 --> 00:04:34.400
Jon: You folks at home- you're the ones who suggested this!

